    $d u v w x y z M $.
    latdisd.b $e |- B = ( Base ` K ) $.
    latdisd.j $e |- J = ( join ` K ) $.
    latdisd.m $e |- M = ( meet ` K ) $.
    $( Lemma for ~ latdisd . $)
